Account Opening Documents (AOD)

These are the terms and conditions by which Windsor Brokers agrees to open and maintain trading accounts for the client and the client agrees to comply with. Included within are: Client Account Agreement, Online Access Agreement, Mobile Trading Agreement and Risk Disclosure Statement.

Trading Conditions (TC)

This document that provides an overview in regards to trading conditions related to financial instruments such as: margin required for trading, leverage, costs etc., prior to clients’ trading. The document should be read in conjunction with the AOD.
